# Plans

- Always store plans in the repo at `.cursor/plans/` (NOT in the global Cursor plans directory)
- Use `.plan.md` extension with YAML frontmatter (name, overview, todos with id/content/status)
- Use descriptive kebab-case filenames (e.g. `second-round-gap-analysis.plan.md`)
- Todos must be comprehensive and actionable -- include specific file paths, line numbers, and what to change
- Plans are version-controlled alongside the code they describe
